data.description: Check out this Beautiful Custom-built home at the Lonesome Dove subdivision! Property sits on 2.5 Acre. Circle driveway with an 20/30 Workshop in the back . Home features 4 bedrooms 3 full bathrooms with the guest bathroom having access to the Patio area. A separate formal dining with a breakfast nook, the master bathroom has a soaker tub with no drains. 2-car garage in the garage has its own closet space with water heater, utility sink, and water softener extra storage space. Don't miss out!
